{
  "stem": "17001.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the-- these people, when they came in, those three, four mens, they started to say it in Yiddish, all the young mothers give their children to the-- to the grandmothers or to somebody-- older person.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Do not take your children with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Do not take your children with you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just take-- leave all your bundles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leave all your packages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just go, go, go down, as fast as you can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't worry about the packages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You will get it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You will be resettled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You will get the packages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just leave the small children to the older people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were dazed, because we were traveling and we were squeezed up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the meantime, we had some dead people in the train, so they pushed it on the side and they were sitting on it, because there were no room for a stiff body to take up that much room.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were really like shaken up sort of.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then when we got out of the-- the wagon and we were marching, they said that all the men go on one side and all the women go to the other side.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my older brother Philip took my younger brother Charlie with him and he put him on his shoulder, because we didn't find one of his shoes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As we were getting off, we didn't find one of his shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So as we were walking, I see that there is a big floodlight.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a very well-dressed German soldier is there, standing there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And meantime, my brother came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he gave my younger brother-- Philip came back and he gave my younger brother Charlie to my mother, because he said, they told me to give the children back to the mother.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
